"Main_Content":
"http://www.slamonline.com/nba/kevin-garnett-shocked-kyrie-irving-opted-surgery/

Kevin Garnett Shocked Kyrie Irving Opted for Surgery

Kevin Garnett couldn’t believe that Kyrie Irving agreed to undergo
season-ending left knee surgery with the NBA playoffs just around the corner.

KG wishes the Boston Celtics had pushed their All-Star point guard to play
through the pain.


KG對於KI在季後賽馬上開始前做出開刀的選擇感到不可置信

KG還希望青賽應該要對KI施壓
"Time":
要他帶傷上陣

以下是KG訪問

“Are you shocked by the Kyrie decision for surgery?’’ [Garnett] asked
"Max_Word_Indicator":
referencing Celtics guard Kyrie Irving’s recent season-ending surgery on his
knee.

I told him I was not surprised
column6:
given that Irving was clearly playing through
pain and there seemed to be some mystery about the whole situation.

“I was shocked. I was totally not ready for that one
column8:
who
battled knee injuries during his time with the Celtics.

“I wish they’d pushed the onus [on him] to play a little bit
column9:
but everyone
is a lot more into wellness and their body these days. In a different era
column10:
maybe you were looked at a little differently [if you couldn’t play through
an injury].’’

KG問記者怎麼不對KI動手術感到驚訝

記者回他KI明顯就已經帶傷打了快一季了
column12:
也許有些難言之隱.

KG說他很震驚
column13:
他還沒準備好接受這個消息.當年他就曾帶著膝傷為球隊打完整季.

KG說希望球隊施壓KI
column14:
但是現在大家比較關心身體健康

在那個年代，如果不能帶傷打，可能是比較與眾不同。

--
